Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  塞兹边境的无人之地出现了罗马大军？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的枪声是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到罗马兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我队将与展开于国防线的第一第三师团汇合…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我就要开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐  请让部下们退到晓时堡辖外
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TITLE-------------------
